name: Mazey Boye
description: Navigate the maze to find the key and bring it all down. The map is super foggy so be warned, navigation is difficult, And a single door needs to be destroyed in order to get to the key, it's pretty close to the start. To get out: find the key, pick it up, and jump through one of the walls within the key area. (it make take a couple jumps, it's fidgety).
